Module com.cab302.wellbeing.model
Package com.cab302.wellbeing.controller

Class InternetExplorerController

java.lang.Object
com.cab302.wellbeing.controller.InternetExplorerController
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.fxml.Initializable
public class InternetExplorerController extends Object implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
This class is responsible for controlling the Internet Explorer. It provides functionalities such as loading a page, refreshing the page, zooming in and out, navigating back and forward, and storing browsing data.
